abilities.name: Bloodied Terror
abilities.rule: At the start of the Fight phase, each enemy unit within Engagement Range of this model must take a Battle-shock test, subtracting 1 from that test if that enemy unit is Below Half-strength.

abilities.name: Swooping Predator
abilities.rule: Each time this model ends a Normal move, you can select one enemy unit that it moved over during that move and roll six D6: for each 4+, that enemy unit suffers 1 mortal wound.
